name: Xaverielle
greetingText: I bet you don't know how much I freaking love your sperm eyes!
wishText: Hi sebyang ko, I made another website for you again, kasi na sad ako sabi ko, ano yun wala nang pakulo ang isang Mark Uchi ngayon valentines day dahil nag early celebrate na? I love you so much baby ko I hope you know that, you literally mean everything to me, and I will always be here to support you in everything, sa pag iyak mo, pag tawa, pagka gutom at iba pa. mamu!
